{"tid":1381509,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"籌錢！站出黎！#多謝香港警察支持捐款","createTime":"2019-07-29T09:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T09:01:48.000Z","uid":280438,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cdb2029a5d4f2be2cdb2e1d3def60f60a8914569","tid":1381509,"uid":280438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:00:48.000Z","msg":"最近去咗書局睇一堆關於抗爭嘅書<br />\n好想睇下和理非可以做多啲乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n第一波係 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#多謝警察支持捐款</span></span></strong><br />\n仿效德國嘅非暴力示威方法<br />\n<br />\n為每個警察做的做一個清單，然後跟據警方數字，或自行決定是從報章或網媒看到的資料，每個細項捐$10，並把捐款全數捐畀<strong>會幫義士既機構</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n如：<br />\n1. 拒發不反對通知書 <br />\n2. 警棍打示威者 <br />\n3. 橡膠子彈 (&times;幾發)<br />\n4. 催淚彈 (&times;幾發)<br />\n5. 海綿彈 (&times;幾發)<br />\n6. 其他可以提出<br />\n<br />\n每次捐出的款項也寫著<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#多謝警察支持捐款</span></strong><br />\n(如果可以把多謝警察捐款的總收據寄番比警總更好)<br />\n<br />\n藉此記錄警察的惡行，同時推動更多人援助義士。<br />\n<br />\n我們不能替前線受傷，但能和他們一起經歷。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，一個都不能少。"},{"pid":"303e6f9be2ceb5ebe3eb1c8c9c96e6fbd0f6a6d3","tid":1381509,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:01:24.000Z","msg":"[推上國際] 防暴警推跌外國婦 施施然離開<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1381423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1381423</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bafee24e57dcf2167d14116fd83c185ea2d15c38","tid":1381509,"uid":87116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:01:27.000Z","msg":"［禍不及妻兒］Pokemon Go式全民搵仔（再開過）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1376102\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1376102</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8a5153dcfe8d841e1f017a6d91e19767312893e0","tid":1381509,"uid":229019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:01:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WMV3tnr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWMV3tnr.png&h=77fc1786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"h